  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,24,"Those opposed, if any."
  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/21eyring,President Henry B. Eyring,25,Thank you for your continued faith and prayers in behalf of the leaders of the Church.
