  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/24porter,Susan H. Porter,37,"See Neill F. Marriott, “Abiding in God and Repairing the Breach,”EnsignorLiahona, Nov. 2017, 11: “Perhaps our life in a loving premortal world set up our yearning for true, lasting love here on earth. We are divinely designed to give love and be loved, and the deepest love comes when we are one with God.”"
