  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/24porter,Susan H. Porter,40,"See Linda S. Reeves, “Worthy of Our Promised Blessings,”EnsignorLiahona, Nov. 2015, 11: “I believe that if we could daily remember and recognize the depth of that love our Heavenly Father and our Savior have for us, we would be willing to do anything to be back in Their presence again, surrounded by Their love eternally.”"
