  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/37nash,Elder Marcus B. Nash,29,"See “The Family: A Proclamation to the World,” ChurchofJesusChrist.org; see alsoJob 38:4–7;Acts 17:29;Romans 8:16–17;Hebrews 12:9;Abraham 3:18–25."
