  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/43renlund,Elder Dale G. Renlund,39,"President Russell M. Nelson has said, “The Lord loves effort” (in Joy D. Jones, “An Especially Noble Calling,”EnsignorLiahona, May 2020, 16)."
  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/43renlund,Elder Dale G. Renlund,40,"See4 Nephi 1:15. There are those who have achieved this kind of unity. In Enoch’s day, “the Lord called his people Zion, because they were of one heart and one mind, and dwelt in righteousness; and there was no poor among them” (Moses 7:18)."
