  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/46cook,Elder Quentin L. Cook,41,"SeeDoctrine and Covenants 1:35. President Wilford Woodruff declared this in 1894 and again in 1896 (seeThe Discourses of Wilford Woodruff, sel. G. Homer Durham [1946], 251–52; see also Marion G. Romney, in Conference Report, Apr. 1967, 79–82; Ezra Taft Benson, “The Power of the Word,”Ensign, May 1986, 79–80; Dallin H. Oaks, “Preparation for the Second Coming,”EnsignorLiahona, May 2004, 9)."
