  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/47nelson,President Russell M. Nelson,42,"So that “when the devil [sends] forth his mighty [wind], … it shall have no power over [us] … because of the rock upon which [we] are built, which is asure foundation, a foundation whereon if men build they cannot fall” (Helaman 5:12; emphasis added)."
