  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/51gong,Elder Gerrit W. Gong,48,"Trust is an essential element of human capital in society and contributes to economic, social, and political prosperity and well-being (see, for example, Francis Fukuyama,Trust: The Social Virtues and the Creation of Prosperity[1995], 3–59)."
