  2021,"10",/general-conference/2021/10/53perkins,Elder Anthony D. Perkins,56,"Twenty years ago, the Apostle Elder Neal A. Maxwell was pondering his painful and ultimately life-ending illness. The Spirit whispered, “I have given you leukemia that you might teach my people with authenticity” (see Bruce C. Hafen,A Disciple’s Life: The Biography of Neal A. Maxwell[2002], 562)."
